{"tid":2478974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連衞兵係咪鬥黃上腦 cctvb個記者都係打份工姐 搞人做乜嘢","createTime":"2021-04-07T12:48:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T14:17:17.000Z","uid":25240,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"32b808e1c70c2a2febe0ad96282e02ca69f17e68","tid":2478974,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"有冇人知呢班係王俊彥跳船個陣係咁用「打份工」黎幫手開脫既on9雙重標準垃圾去曬邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪縮返曬入佢地老母個閪度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個係王俊彥可以睇一睇我呢個po先<br />\n前cctvb 讀稿機 831太子當晚有份直播<br />\n留意返 直播姐係冇 後製剪頭剪尾/ 跟稿讀<br />\n全部都係佢當下見到乜就講乜<br />\n<br />\n（有片）CCTVB 辭左職個王俊彥831太子有份直播 當時話只係見到班速龍揮舞警棍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2462154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2462154</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. Cctvb前線無實權論<br />\n二戰納粹集中營個班軍官都冇「實權」<br />\n因為滅絕猶太人order 由希特拉 &gt; 希姆萊直接落去<br />\n如果cctvb 班走狗諗住用呢套「無權論」黎平反 <br />\n最無辜就一定係振美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再者 <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">落order 條友係仆街 =/= 執行條友係好人</span></span><br />\n「迫」 係一件事 你亦有你既權利去將槍口抬高5cm <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTqCJssvs7NeuBBkCX16WNuBkkfHdrvLBzFfULvCA96Kb?filename=91X1fq9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91X1fq9.png&h=857c6041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 典型偷換概念 + 無限延伸<br />\n用大氣電波日日維穩抹黑<br />\n換返二戰同戈培爾根本冇分別<br />\n<br />\n指正佢呢種邏輯錯誤就上綱上線屌返轉頭唔屌人坐黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>佢依家係咪林鄭阿連衛兵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你就梗係接受唔到啦<br />\n你當人地係林鄭<br />\n又係果d咩平凡之惡論支持者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩阿佢同罪阿ma<br />\n喂你快d每日去黨鐵門口批鬥埋搭黨鐵果班殺人犯啦<br />\n佢地同罪架<br />\n唔好放過佢地<br />\n仲有班貼左安心出行既黃店<br />\n佢地有良心就應該執左佢<br />\n依家佢地協助收集個人資料去逼害香港人<br />\n唔係接受到阿？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcsibrzx9CvemdEyQiZyMobPPJdDbgXDqg77Bs8nqfKFv?filename=J4KppEu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4KppEu.png&h=45420b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaKDvLBHYmw1WVMpWGW65fRyGKHndyedexaZJbyTwRvZG?filename=2qq4pE2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qq4pE2.png&h=8701fb0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXcGr5bf8cAk8vwFaRtr5KcVnwo1RDsAibjN7sfVSX9xP?filename=EcqPAML.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEcqPAML.png&h=b9c6dc19&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 屌cctvb 點解唔屌考新聞主任個班<br />\n講到口都臭撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為cctvb離職個班係考popo囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXEAGVuvGK5YHfiyBQvGUEpzicacqd7Tmvj6pC9dhTq29?filename=eEW3Fgq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEW3Fgq.png&h=b2c8eb20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSwxuhdkDqWQTRt5nrG3c5N88Ew9HwC6CgapHFBoJhXek?filename=CoeT2vc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoeT2vc.jpg&h=88a89325&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPnsQo85VTnPyxz7n3TtDyasGiR9PHRynAFxVjqLwsm3x?filename=dr9MC3C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdr9MC3C.jpg&h=4b18a0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYr8EgAJLkVFQEuTPDFUS2sP3poptNJvrffew64momsz7?filename=ZBX2VQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBX2VQn.jpg&h=23604ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTCx3U6iYqbMaAAigdwaXWYvZVcXcNojAyCgRyWFDMXHE?filename=QD9wPau.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQD9wPau.jpg&h=daaba2b0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾經 當我前年見到cctvb班賤種又扮慘既時侯<br />\n連FB 班友都一面倒叫佢地有份同流合污既咪再扮可憐<br />\n估唔到2年唔洗已經變返「打份工」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重要比呢班智障屌返「鬥黃」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXi8gMCDaN9HgTWzRM6Zpbz5AuuNCSFB7kMe5X3cQthv6?filename=PAu49ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAu49ce.png&h=226a4b43&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXFpioVgtY8YDSCgeeewX68k3ZDUeQBiMDuhD3pMVXnbp?filename=DrUkHxf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDrUkHxf.png&h=ad21be26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUxQDVAF9XkLoBxRBXcoo7xiJGyZJ54nvjnXcvZ2oB2r9?filename=2V2uASg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2V2uASg.png&h=5c1a3ad6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3031551bf4bc6fd3165eae679a5f488264cfdf8","tid":2478974,"uid":55552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:49:50.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bccefa3d6df5fb5dc9de520b3ad8ffc9269536a","tid":2478974,"uid":25240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f3031551bf4bc6fd3165eae679a5f488264cfdf8","tid":2478974,"uid":55552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:49:50.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"純粹見班撚樣雙重標準我先回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3581c4caa3a72ec4b6cbb1e2dc14c97eac904f0","tid":2478974,"uid":47021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on99 唔通黑驚831 打完人之後跳翻出黎又要當佢白驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做得中共走狗 黑驚黑記 唔好諗坐走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903725f5dc4116a64487f369bfce9f49ae7d9b3a","tid":2478974,"uid":196968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"如果條友一個轉身入正苦/黨媒 咁呢班人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c10b76f50f961c3355473a4945a1297765cd203","tid":2478974,"uid":84668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:54:37.000Z","msg":"CCTVB沒有一個是MUSHROOM的"},{"pid":"b89d2f2cb588a27c71d2c2645982ea8140631ade","tid":2478974,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"903725f5dc4116a64487f369bfce9f49ae7d9b3a","tid":2478974,"uid":196968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"如果條友一個轉身入正苦/黨媒 咁呢班人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"叛徒"},{"pid":"bc3ad8c1207906fabb0129318dd51c8b7c39c1f8","tid":2478974,"uid":300690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"林奠都係打份工姐"},{"pid":"e54b07ad8cdd225e0cf4d6add0ad6681d8cb0030","tid":2478974,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89d2f2cb588a27c71d2c2645982ea8140631ade","tid":2478974,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"903725f5dc4116a64487f369bfce9f49ae7d9b3a","tid":2478974,"uid":196968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"如果條友一個轉身入正苦/黨媒 咁呢班人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"叛徒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"寫錯 走狗"},{"pid":"52